{"tid":1228180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你聽日打算買花，入一入黎","createTime":"2019-06-15T16:29:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T20:02:47.000Z","uid":23829,"like":102,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"019adae6ee4be9d775801e61e113ae8b213289e8","tid":1228180,"uid":23829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:29:41.000Z","msg":"我明白獻花係一份心意，<br />\n真花睇落又真係比紙花得體d<br />\n如果你真係選擇買花，請注意以下幾點<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1.確保間花店唔係紅底，唔肯定既話，寧願唔買</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2.咁大件事，d花店應該都知，可能會有有heart嘅花店會平賣/派發白花，請大家褒表佢地，以後多d幫襯</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3.就咁要朵花就夠，唔好包膠/包紙</span></span>"},{"pid":"e221acbc3f5e0f80a917c8d9c595d4656ce2cbbf","tid":1228180,"uid":23829,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:32:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7bd9ae70eabea4e1d8482a612563948be30308","tid":1228180,"uid":23829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:34:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a9871873203e31ee243204f0ac49d05845322a5","tid":1228180,"uid":207942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:36:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8355e257b4d475f547a9563891c0135798a49085","tid":1228180,"uid":23829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c590d28eb9f399dce6a4be9cfa9e9cd18695b519","tid":1228180,"uid":23829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:39:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bf2da42000ab122add2bb77efcc390f348385c8","tid":1228180,"uid":23829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s